### **Violation Details:**

**File:** `lib/features/qr_scanner/presentation/bloc/qr_scanner_bloc.dart`

**‚ùå VIOLATION:**
```dart
class QrScannerBloc extends Bloc<QrScannerEvent, QrScannerState> {
  final CardRepository _cardRepository;
  final AuthBloc _authBloc; // ‚ùå FORBIDDEN: BLoC depending on another BLoC
  
  QrScannerBloc(this._cardRepository, this._authBloc) // ‚ùå WRONG: BLoC dependency
```

**‚ùå VIOLATION in DI Module:**
```dart
